pid":"043270578b14319e44a568ed87e734edc2cf4015","tid":483173,"uid":18565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T02:23:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想知有幾多大學生可以自掏腰包比得起六位數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每人兩萬幾真係有心想做好件事點會拎唔出<br />\n反而佢地係有呢個心唔怕蝕錢肯拎出黎真值得讚賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你叫d返緊工ge每人拎一皮野出黎都冇乜幾多個肯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同人用兩皮野擺落啲9成都返唔到本既野到心信無咩邊個肯"},{"pid":"1a798f01b69ad448ca7920b0089fbc8044fcc92e","tid":483173,"uid":18565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T02:56:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a085715f4c2ae77fbb127c8d94d5b86e36ef57","tid":483173,"uid":110163,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T03:09:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想知有幾多大學生可以自掏腰包比得起六位數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個重點可唔可以放返喺人地創作度</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連登真係多低端<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4個人拿9皮 自己幫人補習 借銀行都有啦<br />\n<br />\n同埋明顯件作品 唔係用父幹可以做到<br />\n俾多幾百萬 冇佢地d心機 創意 同才能 都整唔到啦"},{"pid":"7b8242a7effa686a0aa9a894933ead91bf329ef7","tid":483173,"uid":92603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T03:09:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想知有幾多大學生可以自掏腰包比得起六位數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每人兩萬幾真係有心想做好件事點會拎唔出<br />\n反而佢地係有呢個心唔怕蝕錢肯拎出黎真值得讚賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你叫d返緊工ge每人拎一皮野出黎都冇乜幾多個肯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同人用兩皮野擺落啲9成都返唔到本既野到心信無咩邊個肯</blockquote><br />\n大學生 兩萬幾都真係幾多<br />\n<br />\n真係