ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c35c195dc03b52255befc34647d840494f622b","tid":483173,"uid":22422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T07:37:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想知有幾多大學生可以自掏腰包比得起六位數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係下下講錢嘅話<br />\n人哋拎到十皮 叫好又叫座<br />\n收益點都唔止十皮啦呀嘛？<br />\n比著係第二個人投資十皮？<br />\n又係問邊隻冧把買得過？<br />\n香港收緊皮真係有原因"},{"pid":"45352652a85e32f74b1e7118c36450be1218a236","tid":483173,"uid":8426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T07:42:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想知有幾多大學生可以自掏腰包比得起六位數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除左個政府外 香港咁唔多元化都係多得你呢班契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我意思係如果有錢，可能香港有唔少人有能力拍多D有質素既作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每人2萬幾又算得幾多呀 <br />\n去少次旅行買少幾個袋都有啦"},{"pid":"761935d8e4385f5f1d5b55b2761cdb0bccf6fcad","tid":483173,"uid":93217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T07:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加油"},{"pid":"2374827a0d576303f8adf9406903e782b1d7e59f","tid":483173,"uid":49208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T12:34:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70dd3e9b2f60a3aba75aecaa00e8d88169e6c064","tid":483173,"uid":18565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:20:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推</blockquote><br />\n大大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7734b2e151ea6b672df0e2cdcd27ec4f4222b073","tid":483173,"uid":68641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:23:50.000Z","msg":"埋大仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />